headline: Marriott International (MAR): Assessing Valuation Following Launch of Series Brand with Five New U.S. Conversions
summary: Marriott International (MAR) has signed agreements to convert five FOUND Hotels locations in Miami, Santa Monica, San Francisco, Chicago, and San Diego to its new Series by Marriott line. This marks the Series brand's U.S. debut as Marriott seeks to diversify its portfolio in key cities. See our latest analysis for Marriott International. Alongside the Series by Marriott debut, Marriott International has seen subdued share price movements recently, with investors adopting a cautious outlook...

headline: American Express debuts ad network boasting contextual targeting prowess
summary: Tumi, which piloted Amex Ads, saw return on ad spend 30% higher than its targets while reaching more Gen Z and millennial customers.
